# Long-Term Memory

This file stores curated facts the bot learns over time. It is loaded into the system prompt for every conversation.

Memory updates happen automatically via `[MEMORY_UPDATE]` tags in bot responses. You can also edit this file manually.

## Format

```markdown
## Section Name
- Fact or preference
- Another fact with [date] if relevant

## Another Section
- More facts
```

## Guidelines

- Keep entries concise — this is loaded into every prompt
- Remove outdated entries periodically
- Group by topic, not chronologically
- Don't store secrets here (it goes into the LLM context)

---

Copy this file to `MEMORY.md` to start building your bot's memory.
